                     <interp inst="t18250519-89-off535" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18250519-89-off535" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18250519-89-cd536" type="crimeDate">7th of May</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18250519-89-off535 t18250519-89-cd536"></join>, a watch, value 3 l.; a seal, value 2 s. 6 d., and a key, value 2 s., the goods of 
                     <persName id="t18250519-89-victim523" type="victimName">
                        William 
                        Jones
                     <interp inst="t18250519-89-victim523" type="surname" value="Jones"></interp>
